title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 25 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 25 2022
description:
Former Georgia Senator Kelly Loeffler and spokeswoman for Greater Georgia, the state’s first-ever conservative voter registration group joins C&B to discuss the massive GOP primary voter turnout. ‘Totally predictable’: Beto O'Rourke disrupts Texas Governor Greg Abbott's press conference on Robb Elementary School shooting. Kellyanne Conway, Former 2016 Trump campaign manager, White House senior counselor to President Trump and the author of the new book Here’s the Deal, joins C&B to discuss the Uvalde, Texas shooting, Beto O'Rourke’s campaign stunt and the upcoming elections.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
